      "content": {
        "title": "Osteogenesis Imperfecta and Skeletal Dysplasias — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Genetic disorders of connective tissue and bone matrix causing fragility, deformity, and short stature.",
        "summary": "OI types differ in severity and hearing loss risk. Intramedullary rodding prevents fracture cycles. Bisphosphonates reduce fracture rate in OI."
      },
